text:
Hey guys! What's up it's Ruby and I'm
going to be answering a couple questions

about my favorite things. Okay the first
one is what's your favorite breakfast

food? Bacon and eggs, a big bowl of cereal,
or a smoothie? None of those. My favorite

breakfast food is a spicy breakfast
burrito. It's so bad, but it's so good so
I don't care. Next question. What's your favorite

summer treat? Ice cream popsicles or
watermelon? Watermelon! What's your

favorite thing to do with your friends? A:
go to the beach B: late-night gab fest

which just means like Girl Talk and then
C: dance parties. I think like B or C

mix so if we could have girls talk while
we're having a dance party that would be

my answer. Next question! What are
your favorite types of pics to post on

social media? Glamorous
glam shots, super goofy shots, or family

moments. I don't think I've posted a lot
of glamorous glam shots, but I think

it's a mix between super goofy shots and
family moments. And that's it!
